{"tid":50263,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"win10 自動睡眠 點搞好","createTime":"2016-12-22T09:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T14:22:45.000Z","uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6baca38257c4cf1532b86422ffc25378cbf4ef4","tid":50263,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"上網睇左幾種方法都唔得.<br />\n<br />\n已試<br />\npowercfg -h off<br />\n<br />\n已試<br />\n1.，win+r ，regedit.exe<br />\n2.定位到HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Power\\PowerSettings\\238C9FA8-0AAD-41ED-83F4-97BE242C8F20\\7bc4a2f9-d8fc-4469-b07b-33eb785aaca0<br />\n3.修改attributes的值為2<br />\n4.進入高级電源設置，在睡眠選項中會出現&ldquo;無人参與系统睡眠超時&rdquo;，默為的2分鐘修改成你想要的時間. SET左600分鐘<br />\n<br />\n已試<br />\n高级電源設置：更改高级電源設置&mdash;&mdash;睡眠&mdash;&mdash;允許混合睡眠開啟<br />\n<br />\n全部來源都係大陸網 本身係殘體字見到既都改番做繁體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d023b909aaccd8910bd1c0ed9b7f4f4cd3703ef","tid":50263,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c20932e52426bbdb3edf60a75dda53dcf7212f","tid":50263,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adccc0f9abf41633ca885cee4a7c2928c095cbde","tid":50263,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /